Preconditions:
- The chargeTimes array must not be null.
- The runningCosts array must not be null.
- The budget must be a non-negative value.

Postconditions:
- The method returns an integer value representing the maximum number of consecutive robots that can be run within the given budget.
- If it is not possible to run any robot within the budget, the method returns - If it is possible to run at least one robot within the budget, the method returns the maximum number of consecutive robots that can be run without exceeding the budget.